# =========================
# Secrets
# =========================
backend/.env
backend/.env.*
# .env.prod was previously force-included here (!backend/.env.prod) on the
# assumption it only ever held placeholder values as a deploy template —
# real production secrets ended up committed into it instead. Untracked
# 2026-07-21 (see AUDIT.md); the committed values in git history are still
# live until rotated by hand (Render dashboard, Supabase, Upstash, TMDB,
# Gmail app password) — untracking alone does not invalidate them.

client-mobile/.env.local
client-mobile/.env.production.local

